channel.title: Compiler error Message HELP
channel.description:
Ok so I downloaded the Run Hero source+client it worked great but until I tried to run the compiler I changed this bit:C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.04\bin\javac.exe" to this: C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_04\bin\javac.exe" and it comes up with
Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. Press any key to continue
so could someone download this source and try fixing this for me or could you tell me what is wrong that is making this message appear
Run Hero source page http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,528073.0.html And I mean the source compiler not client compiler BTW I'm completely new to coding ATM
